1. apt update    # Update my server 🔄
2. apt install docker.io    # Install Docker 🐳
3.apt install docker-compose   # Install Docker Compose 🛠️
4 systemctl start docker    # Start Docker service ▶️
5. systemctl enable docker   # Enable Docker service on boot 🔄

Write the compose file, save it, then run the following command:

6. docker-compose up -d
